# CVE-2016-1000027: spring-web HttpInvokerServiceExporter deserialization
# Fixed version: Spring Framework 6.0.0 (Spring Boot 3.x)
#
# Why accepted:
#   This shipping service does NOT use HttpInvokerServiceExporter.
#   It is a legacy Spring Remoting mechanism, deprecated since Spring 5.3.
#   Fixing it requires upgrading to Spring Boot 3.x which is a major
#   migration (Jakarta EE namespace, Java 17 minimum, breaking API changes).
#   Planned for future sprint when application code is updated.
#
# Real-company practice: document accepted CVEs with justification and
# a planned fix date so the security team can audit them.
CVE-2016-1000027
